  "instructions": [
    "Press the tofu to remove excess water.",
    "Heat oil in a pan over medium heat. Add onion and sauté until translucent.",
    "Stir in tomato paste, ketchup, cumin powder, turmeric powder, red chili powder (if using), and garam masala. Cook for about 2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Fold in the tofu and salt, cooking until it's coated with spices and heated through.",
    "Serve hot as a side dish or over rice."
